Benne' caní zaj naque̱' ca tu be' xriwe̱' ca' da quebe dxe'e na nisa, ne ca be' bdunu' bdunu' dxuzría xi na, na' da chul-la chul-la naga naca chee̱', na' Dios guzrá chawe̱' chee̱' benne' ca' naga zaj naca chul-la chul-la chul-la chul-la.
